# JcScreenCapture
JcScreenCaptrue can periodically save screenshots of the computer screen, and supports running in hidden state.


### Features
- Compatible with Win7/Win8/Win8.1/Win10
- Can run in hidden state
- Support auto start and auto hide
- Capture a screenshot every minute
- Compress pictures, keep clarity and reduce disk space
- Save screenshots by date, easy to view
- Automatically clean up files over 10 days


### Download
[JcScreenCapture_Setup_1.0.0.exe](https://github.com/chengjianchun/JcScreenCapture/releases/download/v1.0.0/JcScreenCapture_Setup_1.0.0.exe)


### Install
Run the installer according to the instructions.  
![image][install]


### First run
Run JcScreenCapture after installation, you can set the software to auto start and auto hide.  
The window will be hidden when you click the "Hide" button above the window. Press Ctrl + Shift + J or Ctrl + Alt + J to display the window again.  
![image][firstrun]


### View screenshots

Note: Screenshots will be auto cleaned after 10 days.
